text: Egli Sabin Terry (born 25 November 1991) is a Cuban female volleyball player. She is a member of the Cuba women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Cuban national team at the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship and 2018 Panamerican Cup. == References == == Other websites == * egli-terri globalsportsarchive * Egli Sabin Terry women.volleybox.net Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players
